# Lesson Management System

## Lesson Structure

Lessons organized by physics curriculum in [src/data/physics-units.ts](mdc:src/data/physics-units.ts):

```typescript
interface Lesson {
  id: string
  title: string
  slug: string              // URL-friendly identifier
  unit_id: string          // Physics unit reference
  order_index: number      // Display order
  content: string          // Markdown with KaTeX math
  objectives: string[]     // Learning objectives
  vocabulary: string[]     // Key physics terms
  published: boolean       // Draft vs published
  created_at: string
  updated_at: string
}
```

## Lesson Pages

### Student View
[src/app/lessons/[slug]/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/lessons/[slug]/page.tsx) - Dynamic lesson display:
```typescript
// Fetch lesson by slug
const { data: lesson } = await supabase
  .from('lessons')
  .select('*')
  .eq('slug', params.slug)
  .eq('published', true)
  .single()

// Use MathMarkdown for content rendering
<MathMarkdown content={lesson.content} />
```

### Admin Management
[src/app/admin/lessons/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/admin/lessons/page.tsx) - CRUD interface:
