## Lesson APIs

[src/app/api/lessons/](mdc:src/app/api/lessons/):
- `route.ts` - List and create lessons
- `[id]/route.ts` - Update/delete specific lesson
- `published/route.ts` - Fetch published lessons only

### API Security Pattern
```typescript
export async function POST(request: NextRequest) {
  const session = await auth()
  const userRole = getUserRole(session?.user?.email)
  
  // Only admins can create lessons
  if (userRole !== 'admin') {
    return NextResponse.json({ error: 'Forbidden' }, { status: 403 })
  }
  
  // Process request
}
```

## Lesson Assignment Integration

Link lessons to assignments using `lesson_id`:

```typescript
interface Assignment {
  lesson_id?: string      // Optional lesson reference
  lesson?: {              // Populated lesson data
    title: string
    slug: string
  }
}

// Fetch assignment with lesson
const { data } = await supabase
  .from('assignments')
  .select(`
    *,
    lesson:lessons(id, title, slug)
  `)
  .eq('id', assignmentId)
```

## Lesson Progress Tracking

Track student progress in `student_lesson_assignments` table:

```typescript
interface LessonProgress {
  student_id: string
  lesson_id: string
  status: 'assigned' | 'started' | 'in_progress' | 'completed'
  progress_percentage?: number
  time_spent: number        // seconds
  started_at?: string
  completed_at?: string
}
```